[Result ""]
{SOUTH may have an opening hand, but it is just the wrong kind of hand to respond to

partner's preemptive bid. She doesn't have the immediate winners that NORTH is likely

to need, but she is in good shape for defense should the opponents bid.

In other words, SOUTH has the perfect hand with which to pass.}
